title: Biden to meet with Swedish and Finnish leaders after their nations apply to join NATO - CNN
content:

description: President Joe Biden is scheduled to meet with the leaders of Finland and Sweden on Thursday as part of a show of support by the United States after the two nations submitted their formal applications to become NATO members.
